{"tid":1365831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[升級注意]連儂牆2.0","createTime":"2019-07-25T18:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:33:27.000Z","uid":42691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4470f18adc31dc35faa449f6ebc64d215b72b8","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"［突發］大陸人被迫觀看大埔連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363126</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日黨鐵神助攻<br />\n令到大批大陸人被迫觀看大埔連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我曾經好懷疑連儂牆既實際作用<br />\n但我錯啦 對唔住各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過今日發現連儂牆其實有好大既進化空間<br />\n有幾個諗法<br />\n大家睇下覺得點<br />\n<br />\n1.集中資訊類張貼  揭露官媒同現實既落差<br />\ncctvb遺漏、誤導既真相 <br />\n對官媒既駁斥<br />\n武漢鎮壓既新聞<br />\n該新聞既QR code<br />\n<br />\n2.張貼時應注意邊度係最佳 次要閱讀位置<br />\n現時張貼物品普遍有資訊類 打氣類 恥笑類<br />\n資訊可以擺視線高度 <br />\n打氣恥笑既就建議擺次要位置<br />\n甚至天花 畢竟天花相對難撕<br />\n<br />\n3.打氣類可以讓出最佳閱讀位置 <br />\n同埋可以減少數量 畢竟牆身有限<br />\n但要keep住打氣 畢竟係民意 <br />\n<br />\n4.較大返少少字體 <br />\n大字阿伯阿婆睇得舒服 <br />\n黐高咗低咗 都可以舒服咁閱讀<br />\n路過既行人都可以望兩眼<br />\n<br />\n5.新地方開花 最好一開就遍滿 <br />\n撕紙狗係多 但我發現只要數量多到<br />\n佢地覺得一個人撕唔曬就會好快放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.考慮多用蓮花圖 <br />\n蓮花圖對老人有莫名既吸引力 <br />\n但最近有巴打升級咗長輩圖2.0 <br />\n訊息擺兩邊 <br />\n中間擺泳衣美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.示意可以拎走既文宣***<br />\n細細張可以擺落銀包 或者A5 size搭車睇 <br />\n睇完黐去返工既地方 好似蒲公英咁播種<br />\n<br />\n被捕須知<br />\n基本權利<br />\n常用恰鳩市民既警例<br />\n燈柱分佈地點<br />\n地形圖<br />\nQ&amp;A &lt;&mdash;&mdash;-發現唔係個個巴絲都有辯才 容易被問都口啞啞 建議可以睇定d常見問題 畢竟真理越辨越明或者可以學下點樣用共、官、狗既口吻串返佢地<br />\n<br />\n8.訂立張貼時效<br />\n太多都唔係辦法 畢竟每一日都有新既事發生<br />\n如果覺得允許被撕走既 或者被覆蓋既<br />\n請寫上日期 表明願意讓路<br />\n咁大家就可以覆蓋係老d既張貼上面<br />\n<br />\n9.當眼處應有五大訴求<br />\n話比市民聽 恢復原狀好簡單 就係回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇 大家講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a4f91a0c4907bc99fb82146e998f5d7fc5ec93","tid":1365831,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:31:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0842c4cc735f395622acfc1e43557695f5288083","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:38:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac846ee8be0fda9c25fc5dbf131b9745f6380c7a","tid":1365831,"uid":272668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:39:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e1597cb65c644135cc406b342a29372c933826a","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:56:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36ee139484cda4c3cde1cfd13b586ff1385faa8d","tid":1365831,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:59:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"722361b707986145b787f6f390bd095a847b11dd","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:26:36.000Z","msg":"在外地既巴絲 要做靚香港人呢個品牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365680</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e2476ecfbc588ca46e4ac8e61b18a6742a0dbb2","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:27:09.000Z","msg":"[新疆模式街燈]目前香港街燈有141,400盞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1264811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1264811</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b55c413064270dc0db4fddede03de0a2216944e6","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:06:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a747f89c970bf1663dd3f2be82787f8bcc561130","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"734738264dd89d9e42ef94a18a2e166bb2dd3a1c","tid":1365831,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:11:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24a4b2d17b4b310d9f08d3e395095d76df7e7c8a","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"532b9471c2fe2f53b5f05da4d1c688fc589ab359","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"正經post冇人理"},{"pid":"791dc9dd8cca5d32af32d10d84a326e2527c042e","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88d65c882dc1ca2be68536277dab96543f4c681a","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bf1dbd04b588bab439b36f8ae4224fd3dea816e","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b1a35d8b63766a37ad15d0bb9485c24dae98873","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1648246202123798/posts/2381124852169259?s=1297493134&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1648246202123798%2Fposts%2F2381124852169259%3Fs%3D1297493134%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=8ae029d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1648246202123798/posts/2381124852169259?s=1297493134&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n要說服豬 <br />\n應該要提及飼料 用豬既語言 <br />\n而唔係用宏觀 國際視野 大道理<br />\n<br />\n睇連儂牆既普遍都係 <br />\n師奶阿叔<br />\n應該用佢地既語言 提及佢地關心既飼料"},{"pid":"7f07adca679cf9bbdb9bad77dd3fbdec8a4c52f1","tid":1365831,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT